representative round). Bankroll / bet / last-round badges sit at the top; \
chip buttons adjust the wager; Hit / Stand / Double / Split / Deal sit below \
the hands (each has a single-letter keyboard shortcut). The Options / Coach / \
Shoe & card count / Session openers (collapsed here) expose S17/H17, \
deck-count, basic-strategy advice, Monte-Carlo EV, running count, true count, \
and a cumulative bankroll plot.\"\>",
