    {
     PaneBox[
      StyleBox["\<\"Figure 5. EV(Hit) - EV(Stand) for hard player totals \
12-20 vs dealer upcards 2-A, 500 Monte-Carlo trials per cell. Red (positive) \
= hitting is strictly better; blue (negative) = standing is strictly better. \
The sharp transition at total 17 and the extra band of standing at 12-16 \
versus dealer 2-6 coincide with the discrete H/S boundaries in Figure 4.\"\>",
       
